data.description: Escape to your very own Tuscan retreat in N. McAllen. Single story 4BR/3.5BA For Sale with a spacious open concept floor plan w/3500 SF living w/unique brick & stone exterior & a Tuscan traditional interior design. Fall in love w/the designer vaulted ceilings, marble flooring, exquisite granite counters, luxurious textured & tile adorned walls. Grand living area features built-in movie projector & entertainment center w/mosaic glass trim & cantera stone accents. A beautifully designed Tuscan kitchen is complete with all appliances & custom cabinetry. Home features interior bar w/wine cooler as well as open space to set up your choice of formal living, dining or office/study space. Primary bedroom has its own built-in entertainment wall, ensuite full bath with dual glass bowl vanities, standing oversized shower, jetted tub with large walk-in closet. Split bedroom concept, each with walk-in closets. Lot size is a spacious 0.39 AC w/covered patio & outdoor kitchen w/half bath. Must see!
